headline: Outcomes4Me and Labcorp Study Reveals Digital Education Can Increase HER2-low Awareness for Metastatic Breast Cancer Patients
summary: Outcomes4Me Inc., the developer of the first and only end-to-end, actionable cancer platform, announced today it has been selected to present the results of a biomarker awareness study, conducted with Labcorp, a global leader of innovative and comprehensive laboratory services, at the prestigious 2024 San Antonio Breast Cancer Symposium (SABCS) on December 13, 2024.
